text: William Camp (born October 13, 1961) is an American actor. He became famous for playing supporting roles in many movies such as Lincoln (2012), 12 Years a Slave (2013), Loving (2016), Jason Bourne (2016), Molly's Game (2017), Red Sparrow (2018), Vice (2018) and Joker (2019). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Massachusetts
